        </a>
      </h3>
    </div>
    <div id="collapse_1580455_2" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="1580455_2">
      <div class="panel-body">
        
<div id="content_container_1580465">
<p>When you visit <a href="https://www.salford.ac.uk">www.salford.ac.uk</a> you may notice some Cookies that aren't related to the University. If you go on to a web page that contains embedded content, for example from YouTube, you may be sent Cookies from these websites. We don't control the setting of these Cookies, so please check the third-party websites for more information about their cookies &amp; how to manage them.</p>
</div>

      </div>
    </div>
</div><div class="panel panel-default">
<div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="1580455_3">
