      <div class="panel-body">
        
<div id="content_container_1580469">
<p>You can manage Cookies on the site or at a browser level.&nbsp;</p><p>For information about managing cookies in your browser, please refer to&nbsp;<a href="http://www.aboutcookies.org.uk/managing-cookies">www.aboutcookies.org.uk/managing-cookies</a>.</p><p>Some sites offer the opportunity to refuse cookies for that site. However please be aware that websites use Cookies to improve experience whilst browsing &amp; for certain functionality, so if you disable Cookies you might not be able to use all functions on the site.</p>
</div>

